   <concept id="FAR_25_501" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">25.501</ph> General.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">The contracting officer-</p>
         <ol id="d1631e16" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1653e12">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            Must apply the evaluation procedures of this subpart to each line item of an offer unless either the offer or the solicitation specifies evaluation on a group basis (see <xref href="25.503.dita#FAR_25_503"
                        base="i1091607"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">25.503</xref>);</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1653e20">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            May rely on the offeror’s certification of end product origin when evaluating a foreign offer;</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1654e25">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph> Must identify and reject
                  offers of end products that are prohibited in accordance with 
                     <xref href="Subpart_25.7.dita#FAR_Subpart_25_7"
                        base="i1091171"
                        outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                        class="- topic/xref ">subpart  25.7</xref>;
                  and</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1654e37">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  When trade agreements are
                     involved,
                     must
                  not use the Buy American statute evaluation factors prescribed in this subpart to
                  provide a preference for one foreign offer over another foreign offer.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
</dita>
